# --- Reference / shared inputs (read-only, not shipped as source) ---
# These are handoff inputs from the supervisor; the public repo's own
# source tree lives in src/ etc. Keep them gitignored so they don't leak
# into the published repo.
reference/
shared/
HANDOFF.md
SPEC.md
REPORT.md

# --- Internal build/process docs (not part of the public artifact) ---
