# --- Study / audit notes (NEVER publish) ---
# These are the owner's own study notes and weakness audits. They document
# design debt, wiring gaps, and interview risks in this repo's own code.
# They belong outside the repo entirely; this entry is a backstop against
# an accidental `git add .` before the move is done.
RUNTIME_NOTES*.md
STUDY_NOTES*.md
NOTES*.md
notes/
